Robbers on Thursday night broke into Kilifi Governor Amason Kingi&rsquo;s Nyali residence and stole a laptop and TV set. Yesterday he demanded investigations. Kingi said two AP officers posted at the house were withdrawn. &ldquo;I want to treat it as a normal robbery, but if a person can gain entry into your house, that puts your family members in danger,&rdquo; he told the media yesterday.